                    <li class="collection-item">Close doors and windows when the air conditioner is on.</li>
                    <li class="collection-item">The curtains are made of heat shielding fabric. Close them during the day to keep the room cooler.</li>
                    <li class="collection-item">Use the fans to bring in cool evening/night air.</li>
                    <li class="collection-item">Beach towels are in the laundry room.</li>
                    <li class="collection-item">Large trash item must be tossed in the black trash receptacle in the driveway.</li>
                    <li class="collection-item">Fans can be borrowed as availability permits.</li>
                    <li class="collection-item">Drawing down the large sun shades on the balcony to prevent direct sunlight from entering the room.</li>
